{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"021152aa-968f-4093-ad82-72bc6a9c4a09","content":"This template is **not quite ready** to publish. Key issues:\n\n1. **Missing `$schema`** — Add `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` for validation/IDE support.\n2. **Missing `groupIdentity`** — Recommended for NuGet so multiple versions/languages of the same template are grouped correctly.\n3. **Missing `precedence`** — Useful when multiple versions of the template may be installed.\n4. **Missing `preferNameDirectory`** — Should typically be `true` for project templates.\n5. **No `description`** — NuGet gallery and `dotnet new` listings will show a blank description.\n\nThe core required fields (`identity`, `shortName`, `author`, `classifications`, `tags`) are present, so it would *technically* work, but adding at minimum `$schema` and `description` is strongly recommended before publishing.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"22fef84d-2798-4d51-ba4d-126ac85730c5","outputTokens":204,"requestId":"682B:2EBD1B:4F2E54F:572D36A:69F9F750"},"id":"18bff2bb-0501-4eb5-bb0b-c8febe318eee","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:57:43.125Z","parentId":"9b4fdaa2-762c-45c7-bf0d-ab682e57144f"}
